<div class="navheader"><table width="100%" summary="Navigation header"><tr><th colspan="3" align="center">Software Task - Upgrade From Free To Professional Edition</th></tr><tr><td width="20%" align="left"><a accesskey="p" href="basic_purchase.php">Prev</a> </td><th width="60%" align="center">Chapter 3. Basic Help</th><td width="20%" align="right"> <a accesskey="n" href="basic_manual_activate.php">Next</a></td></tr></table><hr></div><div class="section" lang="en"><div class="titlepage"><div><div><h2 class="title" style="clear: both" id="basic_activate">Software Task - Upgrade From Free To Professional Edition</h2></div></div></div><p>
   There are two simple ways to upgarde <span class="application">Keyman Desktop</span> from the Free Edition to the Professional Edition.</p><h3><a name="id582790"></a>Upgrading Keyman Desktop from the Splash Screen</h3><div class="orderedlist"><ol type="1"><li><p>Open <span class="application">Keyman Desktop</span>.</p><p>
        <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="desktop_images/splash-trial.png"></span>
      </p></li><li><p>From the Splash screen:</p><div class="itemizedlist"><ul type="disc"><li><p>If you do not yet have a licence, click <span class="guibutton">Upgrade to Pro</span> and proceed to purchase. Once you purchase, Keyman Desktop will automatically be upgraded with your licence. You are finished with upgrading.</p><p>
			<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="desktop_images/splash-buy.png"></span>
		</p></li></ul></div></li><li><p>If you already have a license, you can upgrade Keyman from the Configuration menu. Please see below for instructions.</p></li></ol></div><h3><a name="id582857"></a>Upgrading Keyman Desktop from Keyman Configuration</h3><div class="orderedlist"><ol type="1"><li><p>Open <span class="application">Keyman Desktop</span>.</p></li><li><p>Click on the <span class="guiicon">Keyman Desktop</span> icon <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="desktop_images/icon-keyman.png"></span> on the Windows Taskbar near the clock.</p><p>
        <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="desktop_images/menu-free.png"></span>
      </p></li><li><p>Select Configuration from the Keyman menu.</p><p>
        <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="desktop_images/config-activation.png"></span>
      </p></li><li><p>If you do not yet have a licence, click <span class="guibutton">Upgrade to Professional</span> and proceed to purchase. Once you purchase, Keyman Desktop will automatically be upgraded with your licence. You are finished with upgrading.</p><p>
			<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="desktop_images/splash-buy.png"></span>
		</p></li><li><p>If you already have a licence, click <span class="guibutton">Enter Licence Code…</span>. Continue with these instructions.</p><p>
			<span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="desktop_images/splash-activation.png"></span>
		</p></li><li><p>Enter your licence.</p></li><li><p>Click the <span class="guibutton">Activate</span> button.</p></li><li><p>
      Click <span class="guibutton">OK</span>. If you entered a valid licence number, your licence will now be activated. You are finished with upgrading.
      </p></li></ol></div><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3>If for any reason Keyman Desktop refuses to upgrade automatically, you can upgrade Keyman Desktop manually following these instructions: <a class="xref" href="basic_manual_activate.php" title="Software Task - Manually Activate Keyman Desktop">Software Task - Manually Activate Keyman Desktop</a></div><div class="note" style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-right: 0.5in;"><h3 class="title">Note</h3><p>
      The upgrade buttons and links in <span class="guimenu">Keyman Configuration</span> are removed after upgrading.
    </p></div><h3><a name="id583049"></a>What to do if upgrading does not work</h3><div class="orderedlist"><ol type="1"><li><p>
          Make sure that you have entered your licence exactly as shown.
      </p></li><li><p>Be certain that you are entering your licence into the right Tavultesoft product. Keyman Desktop 9 will only upgrade with Keyman Desktop 9 licences. It will not upgrade with Keyman Developer 9 or Keyman Desktop 8 licences.</p></li><li><p>
          You can only upgrade Keyman Desktop on as many computers as the number of licences you have purchased.  See also:
          <a class="xref" href="about_purchase.php" title="Licensing Information">Licensing Information</a>.
      </p></li><li><p>
          If you make a significant hardware upgrade to your computer, you may need to upgrade Keyman Desktop again.
      </p></li></ol></div><h3><a name="id580918"></a>Related Topics</h3><div class="itemizedlist"><ul type="disc"><li><p>
